Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:45.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've wanted this woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had wanted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why go after Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...is MINE!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:02:59.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder why he tried\nto capture Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spider scar\non his back proves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that he is an offshoot\nof Naraku's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way he survived\na direct blow from the Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:04:00.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.\NIt's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It {\i1}should be{\i0} over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll change the poultice later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You needn't be afraid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Muso...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My teacher was killed\nand his face was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was faceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... on his back was\nthe pattern of a spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:48.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spider?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so afraid! So afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take him inside to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A spider pattern on his back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be an offspring\nof Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That demon! What is he up to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, you have reason to\nbe concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:25.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inside you the heart of Onigumo\nbeats steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn that Naraku! How long does\nhe intend to keep me like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to be released?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you! I won't try\nto run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Follow the one\nwho calls himself Muso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Muso?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's new offshoot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And inform Inuyasha and his bunch\nof Muso's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if he would go\nanywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:41.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! How dare he do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is this Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... know... him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just... who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better go back\nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How unusual. You're usually against\nmy going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said you can go this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm worried about my test score,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so if it's all right to go,\NI'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think it's wise for you\nto lie low for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until we know just what\NNaraku is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm uneasy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Nice armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it about this scenery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it really better to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know just who\nthis Muso is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he tried to capture you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Muso was destroyed by\NInuyasha's Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Inuyasha's being\nextra cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's fought several\nof Naraku's offshoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he's never been\nthis cautious before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have an uneasy feeling\nabout this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A cavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we're just\nwalking around in circles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're backtracking the path\nthat Muso took!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should we take a look at the\nvillages he pillaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should go to the site\nwhere the bandits were slaughtered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You! What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I'd tell you\nwhere Muso is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then he's still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why are you here to\ntell us where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:17.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You familiar with the cave where\NKikyo and Onigumo stayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso is headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso's going to that cave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, I told you.\NSee ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:27.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Naraku send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:34.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does Naraku know\NInuyasha's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's enough, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:41.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman!\NWhat's she thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura tried to run away with\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't seem like\nshe's being obedient to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if maybe Kagura\nhasn't told Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about your secret\non the night of the new moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, she's not an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About Muso?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we take Kagura's word\nfor it and believe her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How unusual! Usually, you'd\ntake off right away to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's upsetting you, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Muso... He just bothers me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just don't understand\nthat Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inform Inuyasha and his bunch\nof Muso's whereabouts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And keep watch over him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like he's curious about\NMuso's actions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:56.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean that unlike me,\NMuso isn't under Naraku's control?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you didn't go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I'd better take a look\nat that cave, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right here... someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who... is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's where Onigumo\nonce stayed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:38.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is... where it all began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted that woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... l... was here and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I'll be all right, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... wanted that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if it meant selling my soul\nto demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman... that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Muso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember his aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:46.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't believe it!\NWhy is he here now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way, hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman who is identical\nto Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are the fugitive Onigumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the one you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you won't get me\nthat easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny Kaede, run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:10.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:11.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's just!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looking like Kikyo!\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Why didn't you go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Not you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interfering again, huh, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NWhy are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Muso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That I used to be a bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the time that I stayed here\nin this cave with Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!\NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's Onigumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:14:59.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The bastard who fed his soul\nto demons and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,became the nucleus of Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo's entire body was\nbadly burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even his face was burned away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he kept stealing\nhis victims' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Onigumi's heart burst out\nof Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remembered everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo died back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You wounded Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:37.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you think\NI fed my very soul to demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted possession of the\NSacred Jewel AND a free body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I could steal Kikyo away\nand leave this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when I got my new body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nothing went my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first thing I did when\NI left the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:16:01.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...was to mangle the woman\NI sold my soul for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Naraku was born, Onigumo\nstill had some will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Naraku was created from the union\nof hundreds of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And those demons\nhad one desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The death of my sister,\nthe shrine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the result of all this was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo followed that half-demon\nin death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Sacred Jewel burned away\nalong with Kikyo's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Disappear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:44.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone locked me away\nin a deep, dark place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know\nhow long I slept then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when I awoke, I had been\nhurled into the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He remembered nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even about Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you received no orders\nfrom Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't take orders\nfrom anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just kill everyone I hate,\nthen burn them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, Inuyasha...\NI'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just why are you still alive?\NWhen Kikyo is dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself!\NComing alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After I kill you,\nit'll be that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare touch Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poison insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kaede and Kagome...\nplease get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:43.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know why Naraku\nlet you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you and Naraku are\none and the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I avenge Kikyo's death now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:17:59.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The scar closed on the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see! Muso has the ultimate power\nto regenerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems that your weird sword\nis useless against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Wind Tunnel would've taken\ncare of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does this mean Naraku is\nprotecting Onigumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he sent\nthe Poison Insects
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to prevent me from\nusing my Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:34.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Muso said he takes orders\nfrom no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand Naraku's intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:47.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you\nin person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came to test it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My power right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon who harbors\NOnigumo's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has no power to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right... If I still had\NOnigumo's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to\nlay a hand on you, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if your existence is artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew you're weren't real...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet I was unable to reach out\nto take you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A woman made of clay\nand bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:53.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:20:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not because I fear you\nthat I didn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It suits my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo isn't completely severed\nfrom me yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did he succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His ability to regenerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:20:59.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't believe he can keep\nregenerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Muso said he doesn't take orders\nfrom Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's not under Naraku's control?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:28.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a part of Naraku,\nyet is that possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:35.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That it's useless to no matter\nhow many times you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He resurrected himself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:39.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there a way to destroy him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's transforming even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:56.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm getting used to\nthis body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:21:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:52.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumi's heart was alive\nand continued to beat inside Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku got rid of it\nand it became Muso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's weird, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is trying to\nprotect Muso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why help it if he tried\nto get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is trying to\nabsorb Muso back into his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Muso got his claws\ninto Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:07.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NAre Muso and Naraku enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Three-Sided Battle to the Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The key to it all is\nthat spider on the back!
